"title": "8243: ethics, social",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8243: ethics, social",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture sees ethics as embracing the life of society as a whole, and not simply individual relationships.</p>\n<h2>The benefits of social ethics</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:34\">PRO 14:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:3-2Sam23:4\">2SA 23:3–23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:10-Ps2:12\">PSA 2:10–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:11\">PRO 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:12\">PRO 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:5\">PRO 25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:2\">PRO 28:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:14\">ISA 54:14</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to behave ethically in society</h2>\n<h3>Praying for rulers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:10\">EZR 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:9\">PSA 20:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1\">PSA 72:1</a></p>\n<h3>Submitting to the authorities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:28\">EXO 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12\">DEU 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:6\">1SA 24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:10\">1KI 21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:21\">PRO 24:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:2\">ECC 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:5\">ACT 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:5\">ROM 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Paying taxes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:25\">LUK 20:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:30\">LEV 27:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:28\">DEU 14:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:32\">NEH 10:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:27\">MAT 17:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:6-Rom13:7\">ROM 13:6–13:7</a></p>\n<h2>Specific areas of social concern</h2>\n<h3>Promoting justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:19-Deut16:20\">DEU 16:19–16:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:8\">EXO 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:19\">DEU 27:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">ISA 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:1\">ISA 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:21\">1TI 5:21</a></p>\n<h3>Helping the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7-Deut15:9\">DEU 15:7–15:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:35\">LEV 25:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:39\">LEV 25:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:12\">DEU 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:17\">PRO 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:41\">LUK 11:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:10\">GAL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:3-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:3–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Feeding the hungry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:12\">DEU 26:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:11\">EXO 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">LEV 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">LEV 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:10\">ISA 58:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32\">MAT 15:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:2-Mark8:3\">MRK 8:2–8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:11\">LUK 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:20\">ROM 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:21\">PRO 25:21</a></p>\n<h3>Protecting the vulnerable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22\">EXO 22:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:9\">EXO 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:25\">LEV 25:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17\">DEU 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:1\">PSA 41:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:10\">PRO 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:7\">ISA 58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3\">JER 22:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:16\">JER 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:35\">ACT 20:35</a></p>\n<h3>Peacemaking</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:9\">MAT 5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:20\">PRO 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:18\">ROM 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:19\">ROM 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Showing concern for the environment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">GEN 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:28\">GEN 1:26–1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:2-Lev25:5\">LEV 25:2–25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:31\">NEH 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:16\">PSA 115:16</a></p>",
